OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will begin the evening as a band
OL,7,Fof rain moves southeastwards across
OL,8,Fthe region, clearing around midnight
OL,9,Fto allow for clear spells and a patchy
OL,10,Ffrost to develop. A few isolated
OL,11,Fshowers may linger near the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAfter a chilly start, it
OL,14,Fwill be a dry day with variable
OL,15,Famounts of cloud and bright or sunny
OL,16,Fspells for many. Feeling cooler
OL,17,Fcompared to previous days. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
