OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FUnsettled
OL,6,Fwith an increasing likelihood of wet
OL,7,Fand windy conditions on Friday and
OL,8,Finto the weekend. Risk of gales on
OL,9,FSaturday. Cooler and brighter with
OL,10,Fblustery showers Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
